---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Content from "../../layouts/Content.astro";
const pageScript = "/js/pages/generators/ulid.js";
---
<Layout title="ULID Generator | TechRegistry"><Content title="ULID Generator" titleTag="Generator" starCount="5.0k stars" usageCount="7.7k uses today" version="v2.7.1" statusText="All Systems Operational" freeLabel="100% Free" privacyLabel="Client-Side Only" breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "ULID Generator" }]}><div class="tool-page-shell" id="tool-page-root"><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><div class="tool-toolbar"><button id="tool-load-sample" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" type="button">Load Sample</button><button id="tool-clear" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" type="button">Clear</button><button id="tool-run" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button">Generate</button></div><div class="tool-field-grid mt-3 mb-3"><div><label class="form-label" for="ulid-count">Count</label><input id="ulid-count" class="form-control" data-tool-field="count" value="5" /></div></div><div id="tool-status" class="tool-status">Ready.</div><div class="mt-3"><pre id="tool-output" class="tool-code-output"></pre></div></div></div><div class="card tool-details-card"><div class="card-header"><h3 class="card-title">About This ULID Generator</h3></div><div class="card-body"><p>This ULID generator creates universally unique, time-sortable identifiers for logs, database rows, event streams, distributed systems, and ordered test data.</p><p>ULIDs are often useful when you want IDs that remain unique like UUIDs while also sorting by creation time in many storage, queue, and analytics workflows.</p><ul class="tool-detail-list"><li>Creates lexicographically sortable ULID values.</li><li>Useful for ordered records, event flows, database fixtures, and log correlation.</li><li>Fast browser-side generation powered by the ulid package.</li></ul><div class="tool-points"><a class="tool-point" href="https://github.com/ulid/javascript" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i>Powered by ulid</a></div></div></div></div></Content></Layout><script type="module" src={pageScript}></script>
